    <h2 class="main-heading">Shipping Policy</h2>
    <p class="main-body">Last updated: May 17, 2025.</p>
    <h3 class="all-caps legal-main__sub-heading">Shipping to the U.S.</h3>
    <p class="main-body">We offer shipping to the United States via
      <span class="is--emphasized">UPS Standard International</span>, with tracking provided as soon as your order is dispatched.</p>
    <ul class="main-body">
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Duties & Taxes Included (DDP):</span>
        <br>
        All U.S. orders are shipped
        <span class="is--emphasized">Delivered Duties Paid (DDP).</span>
        This means
        <span class="is--emphasized"></span>duties, taxes, and import fees are included at checkout, and there will be no surprise fees upon delivery. We partner with a third-party service to handle cross-border remittances on your behalf.</li>
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Estimated Delivery Time:</span>
        <br>
        Orders typically arrive within
        <span class="is--emphasized">3–7 business days.</span>
        Please note that delivery times may vary during peak periods or due to customs processing.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Customs Delays:</span>
        <br>
        While all duties and taxes are pre-paid, occasional delays may still occur due to customs inspections. Rewind Skin is
        <span class="is--emphasized">not responsible for shipping delays caused by customs clearance or carrier issues</span>
        once the order has left our facility.</li>
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Canadian Holidays:</span>
        <br>
        Our fulfillment center operates on Canadian statutory holidays. Please note that orders placed around these dates may experience minor delays in processing and shipment. We appreciate your understanding.</li>
      <li>
        At this time, we only ship to select U.S. states. If your address falls outside our service area, you won’t be able to complete checkout.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="all-caps legal-main__sub-heading">Shipping Within Canada</h3>
    <p class="main-body">We ship domestically using
      <span class="is--emphasized">Canada Post’s Expedited Parcel</span>
      service.</p>
    <ul class="main-body">
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Shipping Rates:</span>
        <br>
        Orders of
        <span class="is--emphasized">$149 CAD</span>
        or more qualify for
        <span class="is--emphasized">free shipping.</span>
        <br>
        Orders under $149 CAD ship at a flat rate of
        <span class="is--emphasized">$12.99 CAD</span>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Estimated Delivery Time:</span>
        <br>
        Canada Post estimates delivery within
        <span class="is--emphasized">1–8 business days</span>, depending on destination and local conditions.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="is--emphasized">Delivery to PO Boxes or Remote Areas:</span>
        <br>
        Shipments to PO Boxes and remote locations may take additional time. These timelines are determined by Canada Post’s network.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="all-caps legal-main__sub-heading">Local Delivery (Greater Toronto Area)</h3>
    <p class="main-body">Eligible addresses within select postal codes in the Greater Toronto Area will automatically be offered
      <span class="is--emphasized">same-day or next-day local delivery</span>
      during checkout.</p>
    <ul class="main-body">
      <li>Local delivery is fulfilled via our third-party courier partner</li>
      <li>Availability is based on postal code and appears at checkout only if your address qualifies</li>
      <li>Orders must be placed before the local cutoff time (10am ET) for same-day delivery</li>
      <li>Standard shipping is still available as an alternative at checkout</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
